WEOF		((wint_t)(0xFFFF))
__PCTYPE_FUNC		__pctype_func()
_pctype		(__pctype_func())
_pwctype		(__pwctype_func())
_UPPER		0x01
_LOWER		0x02
_DIGIT		0x04
_SPACE		0x08
_PUNCT		0x10
_CONTROL		0x20
_BLANK		0x40
_HEX		0x80
_LEADBYTE		0x8000
_ALPHA		(0x0100 | _UPPER | _LOWER)
iswalpha	_c	(iswctype(_c, _ALPHA))
iswupper	_c	(iswctype(_c, _UPPER))
iswlower	_c	(iswctype(_c, _LOWER))
iswdigit	_c	(iswctype(_c, _DIGIT))
iswxdigit	_c	(iswctype(_c, _HEX))
iswspace	_c	(iswctype(_c, _SPACE))
iswpunct	_c	(iswctype(_c, _PUNCT))
iswblank	_c	(((_c) == '\t') ? _BLANK : iswctype(_c,_BLANK) )
iswalnum	_c	(iswctype(_c, _ALPHA | _DIGIT))
iswprint	_c	(iswctype(_c, _BLANK | _PUNCT | _ALPHA | _DIGIT))
iswgraph	_c	(iswctype(_c, _PUNCT | _ALPHA | _DIGIT))
iswcntrl	_c	(iswctype(_c, _CONTROL))
iswascii	_c	((unsigned)(_c) < 0x80)
_iswalpha_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _ALPHA))
_iswupper_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _UPPER))
_iswlower_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _LOWER))
_iswdigit_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _DIGIT))
_iswxdigit_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _HEX))
_iswspace_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _SPACE))
_iswpunct_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _PUNCT))
_iswblank_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _BLANK))
_iswalnum_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _ALPHA | _DIGIT))
_iswprint_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _BLANK | _PUNCT | _ALPHA | _DIGIT))
_iswgraph_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _PUNCT | _ALPHA | _DIGIT))
_iswcntrl_l	_c,_p	(iswctype(_c, _CONTROL))
isleadbyte	_c	(__PCTYPE_FUNC[(unsigned char)(_c)] & _LEADBYTE)
MB_CUR_MAX		___mb_cur_max_func()
__mb_cur_max		(___mb_cur_max_func())
__chvalidchk	a,b	(__acrt_locale_get_ctype_array_value(__PCTYPE_FUNC, (a), (b)))
__ascii_isalpha	c	( __chvalidchk(c, _ALPHA))
__ascii_isdigit	c	( __chvalidchk(c, _DIGIT))
__ascii_isalpha_l	c,locale	(_chvalidchk_l(c, _ALPHA, locale))
__ascii_isdigit_l	c,locale	(_chvalidchk_l(c, _DIGIT, locale))
_isalpha_l	c,locale	_ischartype_l(c, _ALPHA, locale)
_isupper_l	c,locale	_ischartype_l(c, _UPPER, locale)
_islower_l	c,locale	_ischartype_l(c, _LOWER, locale)
_isdigit_l	c,locale	_ischartype_l(c, _DIGIT, locale)
_isxdigit_l	c,locale	_ischartype_l(c, _HEX, locale)
_isspace_l	c,locale	_ischartype_l(c, _SPACE, locale)
_ispunct_l	c,locale	_ischartype_l(c, _PUNCT, locale)
_isblank_l	c,locale	(((c) == '\t') ? _BLANK : _ischartype_l(c, _BLANK, locale))
_isalnum_l	c,locale	_ischartype_l(c, _ALPHA | _DIGIT, locale)
_isprint_l	c,locale	_ischartype_l(c, _BLANK | _PUNCT | _ALPHA | _DIGIT, locale)
_isgraph_l	c,locale	_ischartype_l(c, _PUNCT | _ALPHA | _DIGIT, locale)
_iscntrl_l	c,locale	_ischartype_l(c, _CONTROL, locale)
_tolower	c	((c) - 'A' + 'a')
_toupper	c	((c) - 'a' + 'A')
__isascii	c	((unsigned)(c) < 0x80)
__toascii	c	((c) & 0x7f)
__iscsymf	c	(isalpha(c) || ((c) == '_'))
__iscsym	c	(isalnum(c) || ((c) == '_'))
__iswcsymf	c	(iswalpha(c) || ((c) == '_'))
__iswcsym	c	(iswalnum(c) || ((c) == '_'))

min	a,b	(((a) < (b)) ? (a) : (b))

SEVERITY_SUCCESS		0
SEVERITY_ERROR		1
SUCCEEDED	hr	(((HRESULT)(hr)) >= 0)
FAILED	hr	(((HRESULT)(hr)) < 0)
IS_ERROR	Status	(((unsigned long)(Status)) >> 31 == SEVERITY_ERROR)
HRESULT_CODE	hr	((hr) & 0xFFFF)
SCODE_CODE	sc	((sc) & 0xFFFF)
HRESULT_FACILITY	hr	(((hr) >> 16) & 0x1fff)
SCODE_FACILITY	sc	(((sc) >> 16) & 0x1fff)
HRESULT_SEVERITY	hr	(((hr) >> 31) & 0x1)
SCODE_SEVERITY	sc	(((sc) >> 31) & 0x1)
MAKE_HRESULT	sev,fac,code	((HRESULT) (((unsigned long)(sev)<<31) | ((unsigned long)(fac)<<16) | ((unsigned long)(code))) )
MAKE_SCODE	sev,fac,code	((SCODE) (((unsigned long)(sev)<<31) | ((unsigned long)(fac)<<16) | ((unsigned long)(code))) )
FACILITY_NT_BIT		0x10000000
__HRESULT_FROM_WIN32	x	((HRESULT)(x) <= 0 ? ((HRESULT)(x)) : ((HRESULT) (((x) & 0x0000FFFF) | (FACILITY_WIN32 << 16) | 0x80000000)))
HRESULT_FROM_NT	x	((HRESULT) ((x) | FACILITY_NT_BIT))
GetScode	hr	((SCODE) (hr))
ResultFromScode	sc	((HRESULT) (sc))
PropagateResult	hrPrevious,scBase	((HRESULT) scBase)

FD_SETSIZE		64
FD_CLR	fd,set	do { u_int __i; for (__i = 0; __i < ((fd_set FAR *)(set))->fd_count ; __i++) { if (((fd_set FAR *)(set))->fd_array[__i] == fd) { while (__i < ((fd_set FAR *)(set))->fd_count-1) { ((fd_set FAR *)(set))->fd_array[__i] = ((fd_set FAR *)(set))->fd_array[__i+1]; __i++; } ((fd_set FAR *)(set))->fd_count--; break; } } } while(0)
FD_SET	fd,set	do { if (((fd_set FAR *)(set))->fd_count < FD_SETSIZE) ((fd_set FAR *)(set))->fd_array[((fd_set FAR *)(set))->fd_count++]=(fd);} while(0)
FD_ZERO	set	(((fd_set FAR *)(set))->fd_count=0)
FD_ISSET	fd,set	__WSAFDIsSet((SOCKET)(fd), (fd_set FAR *)(set))
timerisset	tvp	((tvp)->tv_sec || (tvp)->tv_usec)
timercmp	tvp,uvp,cmp	((tvp)->tv_sec cmp (uvp)->tv_sec || (tvp)->tv_sec == (uvp)->tv_sec && (tvp)->tv_usec cmp (uvp)->tv_usec)
timerclear	tvp	(tvp)->tv_sec = (tvp)->tv_usec = 0

IsRecognizedPartition	PartitionType	( ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_BSP) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_DPP) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_FAT_12) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_FAT_16) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_FAT32) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_FAT32_XINT13) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_HUGE) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_IFS) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_MAIN_OS) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_MSFT_RECOVERY) || ((PartitionType) == PARTIITON_OS_DATA) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_PRE_INSTALLED) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_SYSTEM) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_WINDOWS_SYSTEM) || ((PartitionType) == PARTITION_XINT13) )
IsContainerPartition	PartitionType	((PartitionType == PARTITION_EXTENDED) || (PartitionType == PARTITION_XINT13_EXTENDED))
IsFTPartition	PartitionType	((PartitionType & PARTITION_NTFT) && (((PartitionType & ~0xC0) == PARTITION_HUGE) || ((PartitionType & ~0xC0) == PARTITION_IFS) || ((PartitionType & ~0xC0) == PARTITION_FAT32) || ((PartitionType & ~0xC0) == PARTITION_FAT32_XINT13)))

__STRALIGN_H_		
_STRALIGN_USE_SECURE_CRT		1
_WINDOWS_INSECURE_DEPRECATE		__declspec(deprecated)
WSTR_ALIGNED	s	(((DWORD_PTR)(s) & (sizeof(WCHAR)-1)) == 0)
__UA_WCSLEN		ua_wcslen
__UA_WSTRSIZE	s	((__UA_WCSLEN(s)+1)*sizeof(WCHAR))
__UA_STACKCOPY	p,s	memcpy_s(_alloca(s),s,p,s)
WSTR_ALIGNED_STACK_COPY	d,s	{ PCUWSTR __ua_src; size_t __ua_size; PWSTR __ua_dst; __ua_src = (s); if (WSTR_ALIGNED(__ua_src)) { __ua_dst = (PWSTR)__ua_src; } else { __ua_size = __UA_WSTRSIZE(__ua_src); __ua_dst = (PWSTR)_alloca(__ua_size); memcpy_s(__ua_dst,__ua_size,__ua_src,__ua_size); } *(d) = (PCWSTR)__ua_dst; }
ASTR_ALIGNED_STACK_COPY	d,s	(*(d) = (PCSTR)(s))
__UA_STRUC_ALIGNED	t,s	(((DWORD_PTR)(s) & (TYPE_ALIGNMENT(t)-1)) == 0)
STRUC_ALIGNED_STACK_COPY	t,s	__UA_STRUC_ALIGNED(t,s) ? ((t const *)(s)) : ((t const *)__UA_STACKCOPY((s),sizeof(t)))
TSTR_ALIGNED_STACK_COPY	d,s	ASTR_ALIGNED_STACK_COPY(d,s)
TSTR_ALIGNED	x	TRUE
ua_CharUpper		CharUpperA
ua_lstrcmp		lstrcmpA
ua_lstrcmpi		lstrcmpiA
ua_lstrlen		lstrlenA
ua_tcscpy		strcpy
ua_tcscpy_s		strcpy_s

MDM_MASK_BEARERMODE		0x0000f000
MDM_SHIFT_BEARERMODE		12
MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLID		0x000f0000
MDM_SHIFT_PROTOCOLID		16
MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLDATA		0x0ff00000
MDM_SHIFT_PROTOCOLDATA		20
MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLINFO		(MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLID|MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLDATA)
MDM_SHIFT_PROTOCOLINFO		MDM_SHIFT_PROTOCOLID
MDM_MASK_EXTENDEDINFO		(MDM_MASK_BEARERMODE|MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLINFO)
MDM_SHIFT_EXTENDEDINFO		MDM_SHIFT_BEARERMODE
MDM_GET_BEARERMODE	_dwOptions	(((_dwOptions)&MDM_MASK_BEARERMODE) >> MDM_SHIFT_BEARERMODE)
MDM_SET_BEARERMODE	_dwOptions,_bm	(((_dwOptions) &= ~MDM_MASK_BEARERMODE), ((_dwOptions) |= (((_bm)<<MDM_SHIFT_BEARERMODE)&MDM_MASK_BEARERMODE)))
MDM_GET_PROTOCOLID	_dwOptions	(((_dwOptions)&MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLID) >> MDM_SHIFT_PROTOCOLID)
MDM_SET_PROTOCOLID	_dwOptions,_prot	(((_dwOptions) &= ~MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLID), ((_dwOptions) |= (((_prot)<<MDM_SHIFT_PROTOCOLID)&MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLID)))
MDM_GET_PROTOCOLDATA	_dwOptions	(((_dwOptions)&MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLDATA) >> MDM_SHIFT_PROTOCOLDATA)
MDM_SET_PROTOCOLDATA	_dwOptions,_pd	(((_dwOptions) &= ~MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLDATA), ((_dwOptions) |= (((_pd)<<MDM_SHIFT_PROTOCOLDATA)&MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLDATA)))
MDM_GET_PROTOCOLINFO	_dwOptions	((_dwOptions)&MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLINFO)
MDM_SET_PROTOCOLINFO	_dwOptions,_pinfo	(((_dwOptions) &= ~MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLINFO), ((_dwOptions) |= ((_pinfo)&MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLINFO)))
MDM_GEN_PROTOCOLINFO	_pid,_pdata	((((_pid )<<MDM_SHIFT_PROTOCOLID )&MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLID ) |(((_pdata)<<MDM_SHIFT_PROTOCOLDATA)&MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLDATA))
MDM_GET_EXTENDEDINFO	_dwOptions	((_dwOptions)&MDM_MASK_EXTENDEDINFO)
MDM_SET_EXTENDEDINFO	_dwOptions,_extinfo	(((_dwOptions) &= ~MDM_MASK_EXTENDEDINFO), ((_dwOptions) |= ((_extinfo) & MDM_MASK_EXTENDEDINFO)))
MDM_GEN_EXTENDEDINFO	_bearermode,_pinfo	(((_pinfo)&MDM_MASK_PROTOCOLINFO ) |(((_bearermode)<<MDM_SHIFT_BEARERMODE)&MDM_MASK_BEARERMODE))
